           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-xcv-flg-sub      .
       xcv-cls-fls-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * [ocr]                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "CL"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/orc/fls/ioc/obj/iofocr"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
